---
title: Prawn Katsu Bao Buns & Cabbage Salad with Spring Onion Fries
description: This week, our favourite fluffy cloud-like buns are packed with crunchy crumbed prawns, a crisp cabbage salad and a rich katsu
sauce. Bao night is quickly becoming a staple in our home, how about yours?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/679c1efaf932bdda4d4c5c3d-2213676f.jpeg
